import { Avatar, Card, Container, Grid , Icon, TextField, Typography} from "@material-ui/core";
import useStyles from '../../theme/useStyles'
import React from "react";
const RegisterUser = () => {
    const classes = useStyles();
    return(
        <Container className={classes.containermt}>
            <Grid container justifyContent="center">
                <Grid item lg={6} md={8}>
                    <Card align="center" className={classes.card}>
                        <Avatar className={classes.avatar}>
                            <Icon className={classes.icons}>person_add</Icon>
                        </Avatar>
                        <Typography variant="h5" color="primary">Registro de Usuario</Typography>
                    </Card>
                    <form className={classes.form}>
                        <Grid container spacing={2}>
                            <Grid item md={6} xs={12} className={classes.gridmb}>
                                <TextField
                                    label="Nombre"
                                    variant="outlined"
                                    fullWidth
                                />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={6} xs={12} className={classes.gridmb}>
                                <TextField
                                    label="Apellidos"
                                    variant="outlined"
                                    fullWidth
                                />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={6} xs={12} className={classes.gridmb}>
                                <TextField
                                    label="Email"
                                    variant="outlined"
                                    fullWidth
                                    type="email"
                                />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid item md={6} xs={12} className={classes.gridmb}>
                                <TextField
                                    label="Password"
                                    variant="outlined"
                                    fullWidth
                                    type="password"
                                />
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </form>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    );
};
export default RegisterUser;
